@page "/table"


<h3>Favorite Movies</h3>

<table class="table table-striped table-dark">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">#</th>
            <th scope="col">Animated</th>
            <th scope="col">Action</th>
            <th scope="col">Horror</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <th scope="row">1</th>
            <td> Megamind [A+]</td>
            <td> Inception [C+]</td>
            <td> Signs [B-]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th scope="row">2</th>
            <td> Lego Batman [B+]</td>
            <td> Count of Monte Cristo [S tier]</td>
            <td> The Sixth Sense [C-]</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

@* search textbox *@
<input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Type here">

<h3>Course Schedule</h3>
<table class="table table-striped" id="dataTable">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">#</th>
            <th scope="col">Course</th>
            <th scope="col">Days</th>
            <th scope="col">Time</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr class="bg-primary text-white">
            <th scope="row">1</th>
            <td>College Physics I</td>
            <td>Mon, Wed, Thu, Fri</td>
            <td>8:30 AM – 9:30 AM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-secondary text-white">
            <th scope="row">2</th>
            <td>College Physics I Lab</td>
            <td>Tue</td>
            <td>8:30 AM – 10:30 AM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-success text-white">
            <th scope="row">3</th>
            <td>Data Structures & Algorithms</td>
            <td>Mon, Wed, Fri</td>
            <td>9:30 AM – 10:30 AM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-info text-white">
            <th scope="row">4</th>
            <td>Intro to Web Development</td>
            <td>Tue, Thu</td>
            <td>11:00 AM – 12:30 PM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-warning text-dark">
            <th scope="row">5</th>
            <td>Calculus I</td>
            <td>Mon – Fri</td>
            <td>1:30 PM – 2:30 PM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-danger text-white">
            <th scope="row">6</th>
            <td>Fundamentals of Residence Life</td>
            <td>Fri</td>
            <td>4:30 PM – 5:30 PM</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>


@* w3 school code inspired *@
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
      $("#searchInput").on("keyup", function() {
        var value = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
        $("#dataTable tbody tr").filter(function() {
          $(this).toggle($(this).text().toLowerCase().indexOf(value) > -1)
        });
      });
    });
</script>



Goal: Display information using tables.
Description:

Create at least two tables, such as:

Course schedule or grades

Favorite movies, games, or projects

Include a header row and multiple data rows

@* Use <thead>, <tbody>, and <tfoot> properly *@

Bonus Challenge:
Add a row or column highlighting your best data (e.g., top score, highest value).
